question: Chiu-khiat 'tn̂g-kî che tiâu-bū' ê sió-liân-chiap sî-thè tùi 2005 kàu 2006 ê piàn-tōng cháiⁿ-iūⁿ?
answer: Iûⁿ chit ê kong-si ê tn̂g-kî che tiâu-bū tùi 2005 nî ê $3,451,276 kiám kah 2006 nî ê $3,289,109, lóng-kiōng kiám kah $162,167.

question: 2005 niáⁿ ū chhiau-kòe 750,000 kho͘, 2006 niáⁿ tō piàⁿ bē-té-khì 750,000 kho͘ ê hū-chek sī sio̍h hāng?
2006 nián ê 'total' chè-tāi ê sió-liâu, ū nn̄g-mih hūn sī 'spectrasite credit facility' lâi sán-seng ê? Hō͘ chhut chòe pek-hun-pí, sió-sió-tōa chhiat kàu nn̄g-ê sió-sió-sò͘.
2006年假如 'senior notes net of discount and premium' 的值可以高 10%, 那麼 2006年的 'total' obligation 會是多少, 假如其他值都沒有變化?
Chit ê siau-sek teh kuan-î, chiàⁿ-chúi ê chet-bū koán-lí chiàn-lio̍k, tùi credit facility chham notes, ē-sái chò sím-mih lūn-tîm?
answer: Chit ê su-liāu sī-m̄-sī piáu-sī chu-pī chiàn-lio̍k ê 1 ê khó-lêng piàn-tōng. Credit facility ( 'american tower' kap 'spectrasite' ) ê chha̍t-kiâⁿ kî-ê iâⁿ-chē ti̍t-chiat cheng-ka, chiō-chún nā 'notes' ê chet-bū tō chin chē kiám-sio̍k he̍k-sī siau-chhap. Chit ê ē-sái piáu-sī sī 1 ê chiàn-lio̍k choán-tó koán-lí chet-bū chīn credit facility, ē-tàng ū khah hó ê tiâu-kiāⁿ he̍k-sī kî-tāi, chiō-chún nā oân-chiok kî-ê bô-kâng ê 'notes' kiám-sio̍k he̍k-sī têng-sin khoah-chè.

question: Paiñn ke bat-chuñ kôan-châi ūi-hng ê miâ-chheng, in-ūi ū chi̍t ê nî-thâu bô su-liāu?
answer: senior subordinated discount notes net of discount and warrant valuation
